Definition: Defines the equipment that will be automatically created when a zone is created. Equipment will be sized to serve the zone load.
Defines whether the zone is sized for the cooling loads of the spaces, the heating loads or both.
Indicates how the zone level equipment will be connected to the zone. For ex. a supply side VAV system should select "Supply Side Only". Recirculating systems should select "Closed Loop".
Override for equipment SA temperature in cooling scenarios (optional)
Override for equipment SA temperature in heating scenarios (optional)
